Class AbstractWuicResource

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class AbstractWuicResource
extends Object
implements WuicResource

Base implementation of the WuicResource interface. A WuicResource is often represented by a name and a FileType. This class already manages it.
